! API 문서 스니펫 모음

앞으로 API 문서 작성할 때 편집 모드(연필 아이콘)로 열어서 필요한 부분 복사해서 쓰세요.

복붙 후 아래 3가지를 찾아바꾸기(Cmd+H 또는 Ctrl+H)로 일괄 치환하세요.

|찾기 |바꾸기 |h
|`$_:` |`$:` |
|`[_[` |`[[` |
|`]_]` |`]]` |

---

!! 1. 엔드포인트 카드 (엔드포인트 하나당 반복)

팝업 `$reveal`은 반드시 `api-body` `$reveal` 바깥, `api-card` div 안에 배치하세요.

<pre>
&lt;div class="api-card"&gt;
&lt;$reveal state="$_:/state/api-PROJECT-ID" type="match" text="yes" default="no" tag="div"&gt;
&lt;$button class="api-summary-btn" set="$_:/state/api-PROJECT-ID" setTo="no"&gt;
&lt;span class="api-method api-METHOD"&gt;METHOD&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="api-path"&gt;/YOUR/PATH&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="api-summary-text"&gt;요약 설명&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="api-chevron open"&gt;▶&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/$button&gt;&lt;/$reveal&gt;
&lt;$reveal state="$_:/state/api-PROJECT-ID" type="nomatch" text="yes" default="no" tag="div"&gt;
&lt;$button class="api-summary-btn" set="$_:/state/api-PROJECT-ID" setTo="yes"&gt;
&lt;span class="api-method api-METHOD"&gt;METHOD&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="api-path"&gt;/YOUR/PATH&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="api-summary-text"&gt;요약 설명&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="api-chevron"&gt;▶&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/$button&gt;&lt;/$reveal&gt;
&lt;$reveal state="$_:/state/api-PROJECT-ID" type="match" text="yes" default="no" class="api-body" tag="div"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;설명&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;설명을 여기에&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Request Body&lt;/strong&gt; (&lt;code&gt;application/json&lt;/code&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;$button class="api-schema-link"&gt;&lt;$action-setfield $tiddler="$_:/state/req-PROJECT-ID" text="yes"/&gt;→ SchemaName&lt;/$button&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;{
  "field": "value"
}&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responses&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="api-resp-group"&gt;
&lt;span class="api-resp resp-2xx"&gt;200&lt;/span&gt; 설명
&lt;$button class="api-schema-link"&gt;&lt;$action-setfield $tiddler="$_:/state/resp-PROJECT-ID-200" text="yes"/&gt;→ RespSchemaName&lt;/$button&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;{
  "field": "value"
}&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;span class="api-resp resp-4xx"&gt;400&lt;/span&gt; 설명&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/$reveal&gt;
&lt;!-- 팝업들은 api-body 바깥, api-card 안에 --&gt;
&lt;$reveal state="$_:/state/req-PROJECT-ID" type="match" text="yes" default="no" tag="div"&gt;
&lt;div style="position:fixed;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;z-index:9998;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;"&gt;
&lt;div style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;background:rgba(0,0,0,0.5);" onclick="$tw.wiki.setText('$_:/state/req-PROJECT-ID','text',null,'no')"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style="position:relative;background:#2a2a2a;border:1px solid #444;border-radius:8px;padding:20px;z-index:9999;min-width:300px;max-width:500px;max-height:70vh;overflow-y:auto;box-shadow:0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);"&gt;
&lt;div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;margin-bottom:12px;border-bottom:1px solid #444;padding-bottom:8px;"&gt;
&lt;span style="font-weight:bold;color:#d4d4d4;font-family:monospace;"&gt;SchemaName&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;$button style="background:transparent;border:none;color:#aaa;cursor:pointer;font-size:16px;padding:0 4px;"&gt;
&lt;$action-setfield $tiddler="$_:/state/req-PROJECT-ID" text="no"/&gt;✕&lt;/$button&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class="schema-body"&gt;&lt;&lt;renderSchema dataTiddler:"Project:PROJECTNAME-API-Schemas-Data" schemaName:"SchemaName"&gt;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/$reveal&gt;
&lt;$reveal state="$_:/state/resp-PROJECT-ID-200" type="match" text="yes" default="no" tag="div"&gt;
&lt;div style="position:fixed;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;z-index:9998;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;"&gt;
&lt;div style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;background:rgba(0,0,0,0.5);" onclick="$tw.wiki.setText('$_:/state/resp-PROJECT-ID-200','text',null,'no')"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style="position:relative;background:#2a2a2a;border:1px solid #444;border-radius:8px;padding:20px;z-index:9999;min-width:300px;max-width:500px;max-height:70vh;overflow-y:auto;box-shadow:0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);"&gt;
&lt;div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;margin-bottom:12px;border-bottom:1px solid #444;padding-bottom:8px;"&gt;
&lt;span style="font-weight:bold;color:#d4d4d4;font-family:monospace;"&gt;RespSchemaName&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;$button style="background:transparent;border:none;color:#aaa;cursor:pointer;font-size:16px;padding:0 4px;"&gt;
&lt;$action-setfield $tiddler="$_:/state/resp-PROJECT-ID-200" text="no"/&gt;✕&lt;/$button&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class="schema-body"&gt;&lt;&lt;renderSchema dataTiddler:"Project:PROJECTNAME-API-Schemas-Data" schemaName:"RespSchemaName"&gt;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/$reveal&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
</pre>

